        "message": "LU-5483 tests: perform recovery-mds-scale test\n\nThis is for test only.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly alwaysuploadlogs \\\nenvdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,REQFAIL=100 \\\nmdtfilesystemtype=ldiskfs mdsfilesystemtype=ldiskfs ostfilesystemtype=ldiskfs \\\nclientdistro=el6 ossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nossarch=x86_64 mdsarch=x86_64 clientjob=lustre-b_ieel2_0 clientbuildno=81 \\\nossjob=lustre-b_ieel2_0 mdsjob=lustre-b_ieel2_0 ossbuildno=81 mdsbuildno=81 \\\nclientcount=4 osscount=2 mdscount=2 \\\nmdssizegb=10 ostsizegb=10 austeroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\ntestlist=recovery-random-scale,recovery-mds-scale\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia69497826b96671c30423777ef4cee10c3a4f313\n"
